author: Lego_fan_
title: Already made?
review:
Lego magazine gift set Tie Advanced is perfect for any Lego Star Wars collection.

The set is like all magazine gift sets in the sense that they do not have any instructions which makes it all the more fun. After i built it i checked a youtube video about it just to see if my guess was right. 

It is a fun little build and to only function is that the wings can move forwards for an emergency break that is space would rip the wings off :)

Over all i think this is a fun 'lil set but i feel like it has been made before....
